# A1/A4 end-to-end shell flow for a marker-prefixed + (RomM)-tagged on-card name: the decorated
# path must flow through the save check unmangled and the CURRENT gate must still hold.
desc fetch hook: marker+tag named rom (separate mode shape) -> CURRENT gate silent launch
invoke prehook
config paired
romarg Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda (RomM).gba
sdfile+ Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda (RomM).gba
engine 0|101\t2026-07-01 10:00\tBrick\t32KB\tCURRENT\nLOCAL=current
expect_exit 0
expect_trace_absent LIST[
expect_trace ENGINE --list-saves
expect_log newest=current action=silent
